tees</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 3, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is an amazing plugin offering so many features. The fact that is it so widely used is helpful when seeking additional information. Whenever I have needed help for the free plugin, their community based support has been very helpful. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Shipping Rate - Miscalc</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/freddredirl/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f9415f6ba167f30d0fd23502020fd07b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f9415f6ba167f30d0fd23502020fd07b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/freddredirl/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">freddredirl</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 3, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For anyone else who experience a MAJOR shipping miscalc in v 9.0.1 around 27th Jun 24 then its caused by the , or . settings in Woocommerce&gt;Settings&gt;Currency Options. Depending on what you have in those fields the login in that version of the plugin reversed the processing of the seperators.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Workaround was to round shipping rates up to no decimals until I realised what the cause was. Looks like the code is being rolled back in Woocommece V 9.0.2</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">HI WOO</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jan2525/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ec3a612018b730b07a4e64115ac65c27?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ec3a612018b730b07a4e64115ac65c27?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jan2525/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">jan2525</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 1, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>very bad</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>):</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Woo Sucks, Crashed On Busy Holiday</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/headly/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b068fdb2fcf2b8d02881d5ddfe47f7ed?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b068fdb2fcf2b8d02881d5ddfe47f7ed?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/headly/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">headly</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 1, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tired of plugin conflicts, upgrades that aren\'t tested.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Woo likes to blame themes and other plugins instead of taking responsibility.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I will change my review when they change their upgrade \'behavior\' and posting a change log for all to see.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I wasted 9 hours trying to fix a broken cart that would not allow customers to remove items, change quantities or check out as a guest. Luckily I have other sites with the exact same configuration (call it A/B testing). It turns out Woo changed the short code on my checkout and cart pages.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you have my problem you should look for these codes:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cart: &lt;!-- wp:shortcode -- &gt;[woocommerce_cart]&lt;!--/wp:shortcode --&gt;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Checkout: &lt;!-- wp:shortcode --&gt; [woocommerce_checkout]&lt;!-- /wp:shortcode --&gt;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I had a ton of garbage code on those pages after upgrading plugin to 9.02 that caused the cart to stop working. All on woo for lack of transparency.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Вопрос с ошибкой 403</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/seniorperfiliew/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6a5d12cdc3c4e0fcc689017983dc9672?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6a5d12cdc3c4e0fcc689017983dc9672?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/seniorperfiliew/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Иван Анатольевич <small>(seniorperfiliew)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 27, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Решали долго, так как получал ответы размытые, переписка примерно длилась неделю. Один из последних специалистов, написал все по существу, я выполнил необходимые манипуляции, и получил нужный результат.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">A Wonderful Tool For My Online Store</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/musa70/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/edf1ae942f1c565057e2a0cce4f54584?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/edf1ae942f1c565057e2a0cce4f54584?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/musa70/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">musa70</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 26, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It Does Everything Beyond Imagination..:)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very Helpful</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/makintracks/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/859e6a6c6b30609cfa3601b80994c962?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/859e6a6c6b30609cfa3601b80994c962?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/makintracks/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">makintracks</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 24, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>My first time asking Woo for help and I am so impressed with the assistance I received. Thank you very much for clarifying the issue with the nofollow tags on buttons. It is a relief knowing I have nothing to worry about.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n\";}s:13:\"download_link\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/woocommerce.9.0.2.zip\";s:14:\"upgrade_notice\";a:0:{}s:11:\"screenshots\";a:6:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=2366418\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=2366418\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=2366418\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-4.jpg?rev=2366418\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https:/